{"title":"从零部署私有化搜索引擎：SearXNG 完整指南","uid":"58e6e48d30b9663fc3cb125ce36d3d09","slug":"从零部署私有化搜索引擎-SearXNG-完整指南","date":"2026-04-17T11:45:00.000Z","updated":"2026-04-17T11:48:10.243Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/从零部署私有化搜索引擎-SearXNG-完整指南.json","keywords":"记录, 学习, ClaRnS","cover":"/gallery/tech.png","content":"<p>在数据隐私日益重要的今天，拥有一个可控的私有化搜索引擎不再是技术极客的专属。本文将手把手带你部署 SearXNG，并分享我在实际部署中遇到的坑与解决方案。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"一、为什么需要私有化搜索？\"><a href=\"#一、为什么需要私有化搜索？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、为什么需要私有化搜索？\"></a>一、为什么需要私有化搜索？</h2><p>在使用商业搜索引擎时，我们的搜索记录、点击行为都在被记录和分析。而私有化搜索引擎能给我们带来：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>隐私保护</strong>：搜索记录仅保存在本地，不上传第三方</li>\n<li><strong>无广告干扰</strong>：纯净搜索结果，告别竞价排名</li>\n<li><strong>多引擎聚合</strong>：一次搜索，同时查询百度、360、Bing 等多个引擎</li>\n<li><strong>完全可控</strong>：自己决定收录哪些搜索引擎，过滤什么内容</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"二、SearXNG-简介\"><a href=\"#二、SearXNG-简介\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、SearXNG 简介\"></a>二、SearXNG 简介</h2><p><a href=\"https://github.com/searxng/searxng\">SearXNG</a> 是一个免费的互联网元搜索引擎，它聚合了 70+ 个搜索引擎的结果，保护用户的隐私。相比原版 SearX，SearXNG 更新更活跃，功能更完善。</p>\n<h2 id=\"三、环境准备\"><a href=\"#三、环境准备\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、环境准备\"></a>三、环境准备</h2><h3 id=\"系统要求\"><a href=\"#系统要求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统要求\"></a>系统要求</h3><ul>\n<li>Ubuntu 20.04+ &#x2F; Debian 11+ &#x2F; 其他 Linux 发行版</li>\n<li>Python 3.8+</li>\n<li>至少 1GB 内存</li>\n<li>一个空闲端口（默认 8888）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装依赖\"><a href=\"#安装依赖\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装依赖\"></a>安装依赖</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 更新系统</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">apt</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">update</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&amp;&amp;</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">apt</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">upgrade</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-y</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 安装基础依赖</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">apt</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-y</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">git</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">python3</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">python3-pip</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">python3-venv</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">\\</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">build-essential</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">libxml2-dev</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">libxslt1-dev</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">\\</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">zlib1g-dev</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">libffi-dev</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">libssl-dev</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>注意</strong>：<code>libxml2-dev</code> 和 <code>libxslt1-dev</code> 是编译某些 Python 包的必需依赖，缺少它们会导致后续安装失败。</p>\n<h2 id=\"四、安装与配置\"><a href=\"#四、安装与配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、安装与配置\"></a>四、安装与配置</h2><h3 id=\"1-克隆源码\"><a href=\"#1-克隆源码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 克隆源码\"></a>1. 克隆源码</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 创建工作目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">mkdir</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-p</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/workspace/searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/workspace/searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 克隆源码</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">git</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">clone</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">https://github.com/searxng/searxng.git</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">.</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"2-创建虚拟环境并安装\"><a href=\"#2-创建虚拟环境并安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 创建虚拟环境并安装\"></a>2. 创建虚拟环境并安装</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 创建虚拟环境</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">python3</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-m</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">venv</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">venv</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 激活虚拟环境</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">source</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">venv/bin/activate</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 安装依赖</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">pip</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-e</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 安装额外依赖（用于某些搜索引擎）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">pip</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-e</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&#39;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">.[test]</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&#39;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"3-配置文件详解\"><a href=\"#3-配置文件详解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 配置文件详解\"></a>3. 配置文件详解</h3><p>SearXNG 的配置文件是 YAML 格式，默认位置在 <code>~/.config/searxng/settings.yml</code>。</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 创建配置目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">mkdir</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-p</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.config/searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 创建配置文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">cat</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.config/searxng/settings.yml</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&lt;&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> &#39;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">EOF</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\"># SearXNG 配置文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\"># 通用设置</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">general:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  debug: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  instance_name: &quot;My SearXNG&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  contact_url: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  enable_metrics: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\"># 服务器设置</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">server:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  port: 8888</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  bind_address: &quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  secret_key: &quot;your-secret-key-here&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  base_url: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  image_proxy: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\"># 搜索引擎配置</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">engines:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  - name: baidu</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    engine: baidu</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    shortcut: bd</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    disabled: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  - name: 360</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    engine: 360search</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    shortcut: so</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    disabled: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  - name: bing</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    engine: bing</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    shortcut: bi</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    disabled: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  - name: duckduckgo</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    engine: duckduckgo</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    shortcut: ddg</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">    disabled: false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\"># UI 设置</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">ui:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  default_theme: simple</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  default_locale: zh</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\"># 搜索设置</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">search:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  safe_search: 0</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">  default_lang: &quot;zh-CN&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">EOF</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>关键配置项说明：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>server.bind_address</code>: 设置为 <code>&quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</code> 允许从外部访问</li>\n<li><code>server.secret_key</code>: 用于加密会话，请使用随机字符串</li>\n<li><code>engines</code>: 启用的搜索引擎列表，可根据需要增减</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"4-启动-SearXNG\"><a href=\"#4-启动-SearXNG\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 启动 SearXNG\"></a>4. 启动 SearXNG</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 方式一：直接启动（前台运行）</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/workspace/searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">source</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">venv/bin/activate</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">SEARXNG_SETTINGS_PATH</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.config/searxng/settings.yml</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">\\</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">python</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-m</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">searx.webapp</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 方式二：后台运行</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/workspace/searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">source</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">venv/bin/activate</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">SEARXNG_SETTINGS_PATH</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.config/searxng/settings.yml</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">\\</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">nohup</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">python</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-m</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">searx.webapp</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">searxng.log</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">2&gt;&amp;1</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&amp;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"5-验证安装\"><a href=\"#5-验证安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"5. 验证安装\"></a>5. 验证安装</h3><p>打开浏览器访问 <code>http://localhost:8888</code>，如果看到搜索界面，说明安装成功！</p>\n<h2 id=\"五、踩坑记录\"><a href=\"#五、踩坑记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、踩坑记录\"></a>五、踩坑记录</h2><h3 id=\"坑-1：settings-yml-路径问题\"><a href=\"#坑-1：settings-yml-路径问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 1：settings.yml 路径问题\"></a>坑 1：settings.yml 路径问题</h3><p><strong>现象</strong>：启动时报错 <code>FileNotFoundError</code></p>\n<p><strong>解决</strong>：通过环境变量指定配置文件路径：</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">export</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">SEARXNG_SETTINGS_PATH</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">/home/username/.config/searxng/settings.yml</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"坑-2：依赖安装失败\"><a href=\"#坑-2：依赖安装失败\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 2：依赖安装失败\"></a>坑 2：依赖安装失败</h3><p><strong>现象</strong>：安装时提示 <code>Failed building wheel for lxml</code></p>\n<p><strong>解决</strong>：安装系统级依赖：</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">apt</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">libxml2-dev</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">libxslt1-dev</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">zlib1g-dev</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"坑-3：端口冲突\"><a href=\"#坑-3：端口冲突\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 3：端口冲突\"></a>坑 3：端口冲突</h3><p><strong>现象</strong>：启动时报错 <code>Address already in use</code></p>\n<p><strong>解决</strong>：修改配置文件中的 <code>server.port</code>，或杀死占用端口的进程：</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">lsof</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-i</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">:8888</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">kill</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-9</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">PI</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">D</span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"坑-4：防火墙拦截\"><a href=\"#坑-4：防火墙拦截\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 4：防火墙拦截\"></a>坑 4：防火墙拦截</h3><p><strong>现象</strong>：本地能访问，局域网其他设备无法访问</p>\n<p><strong>解决</strong>：开放防火墙端口：</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">ufw</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">allow</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">8888</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">/tcp</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">ufw</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">reload</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"坑-5：systemd-service-配置\"><a href=\"#坑-5：systemd-service-配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 5：systemd service 配置\"></a>坑 5：systemd service 配置</h3><p>为了让 SearXNG 开机自动启动，可以配置 systemd service：</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 创建 service 文件</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">tee</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">/etc/systemd/system/searxng.service</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&gt;</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">/dev/null</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #CB7676\">&lt;&lt;</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> &#39;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">EOF</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">&#39;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">[Unit]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">Description=SearXNG - Privacy-respecting metasearch engine</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">After=network.target</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">[Service]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">Type=simple</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">User=clarn</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">WorkingDirectory=/home/clarn/.openclaw/workspace/searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">Environment=&quot;SEARXNG_SETTINGS_PATH=/home/clarn/.config/searxng/settings.yml&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">ExecStart=/home/clarn/.openclaw/workspace/searxng/venv/bin/python -m searx.webapp</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">Restart=always</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">RestartSec=5</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">[Install]</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">WantedBy=multi-user.target</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">EOF</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 重载配置并启动</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">daemon-reload</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">enable</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">searxng</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">systemctl</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">start</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">searxng</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"六、与-OpenClaw-集成\"><a href=\"#六、与-OpenClaw-集成\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、与 OpenClaw 集成\"></a>六、与 OpenClaw 集成</h2><p>如果你使用 OpenClaw 作为 AI 助手框架，可以将 SearXNG 配置为默认搜索引擎：</p>\n<p>编辑 <code>~/.openclaw/openclaw.json</code>：</p>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">tools</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">web</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">      </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">search</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">provider</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">searxng</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">searxng</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">          </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">url</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">http://localhost:8888</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">      </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p>重启 OpenClaw Gateway 后，<code>web_search</code> 工具就会使用你的私有化搜索引擎了！</p>\n<h2 id=\"七、进阶优化\"><a href=\"#七、进阶优化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七、进阶优化\"></a>七、进阶优化</h2><h3 id=\"1-添加更多搜索引擎\"><a href=\"#1-添加更多搜索引擎\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 添加更多搜索引擎\"></a>1. 添加更多搜索引擎</h3><p>编辑 <code>~/.config/searxng/settings.yml</code>，在 <code>engines</code> 部分添加：</p>\n<div class=\"language-yaml\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">yaml</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">-</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">name</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">wikipedia</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">engine</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">wikipedia</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">shortcut</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">wp</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">disabled</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">false</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">-</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">name</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">github</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">engine</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">github</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">shortcut</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">gh</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">disabled</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">false</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"2-启用搜索结果缓存\"><a href=\"#2-启用搜索结果缓存\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 启用搜索结果缓存\"></a>2. 启用搜索结果缓存</h3><p>安装 Redis 并配置缓存，可以显著提升重复搜索的速度：</p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">sudo</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">apt</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">redis-server</span></span></code></pre></div><p>然后在配置文件中添加：</p>\n<div class=\"language-yaml\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">yaml</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">redis</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">url</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">redis://localhost:6379/0</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"八、总结\"><a href=\"#八、总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"八、总结\"></a>八、总结</h2><p>通过本文的步骤，你应该已经成功部署了自己的私有化搜索引擎。SearXNG 不仅能保护隐私，还能聚合多个搜索引擎的结果，提供更全面的搜索体验。</p>\n<p><strong>后续可探索的方向：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>与知识库（如 AnythingLLM）联动，实现搜索+问答的完整工作流</li>\n<li>配置 HTTPS，使用域名访问</li>\n<li>添加更多专业搜索引擎（学术、代码等）</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><em>本文基于实际部署经验撰写，如有问题欢迎在评论区留言交流。</em></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"在数据隐私日益重要的今天，拥有一个可控的私有化搜索引擎不再是技术极客的专属。本文将手把手带你部署 SearXNG，并分享我在实际部署中遇到的坑与解决方案。 一、...","permalink":"/post/从零部署私有化搜索引擎-SearXNG-完整指南","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.6k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"技术分享","slug":"技术分享","count":2,"path":"api/categories/技术分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"SearXNG","slug":"SearXNG","count":1,"path":"api/tags/SearXNG.json"},{"name":"私有化","slug":"私有化","count":1,"path":"api/tags/私有化.json"},{"name":"搜索引擎","slug":"搜索引擎","count":1,"path":"api/tags/搜索引擎.json"},{"name":"隐私保护","slug":"隐私保护","count":1,"path":"api/tags/隐私保护.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E9%9C%80%E8%A6%81%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E5%8C%96%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%EF%BC%9F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、为什么需要私有化搜索？</spa